Joma odak e god Nyasaye maler


1  A Ruoth Nyasaye,

ere ng’ama onego odag e Hekalu mari?

Koso en ng’a monego bed e godi maler?


2  Nyaka obed ng’ama oluoro Nyasaye e yore duto,

kendo ma pile timo gik makare,

bende ma wechene gin adier, kendo ma onge miganga.


3  Onego obed ng’at ma ok keth nying ng’ato,

kendo ma ok tim marach ni osiepene,

bende ma ok kuodh jowadgi,


4  to ma charo jogo ma Nyasaye odagi.

Joma oluoro Nyasaye to omiyo duong’.

Pile otimo gima osesingore ni obiro timo,

kata bed ni en gima biro hinye en owuon,


5  Oholo gik moko, to ok okawie ohala,

kendo ok ocham asoya mondo oketh buche joma onge ketho.

Ng’at ma timo gigo duto ok nopodhi.

